# ── ARCHIVE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Local-only reference material moved out of the working tree. This is ignored
# WHOLESALE and deliberately so: Archive/gas-webapp/Code.gs contains the live
# Anthropic API key and the shared admin credentials, and
# Archive/CREDENTIALS.md consolidates every secret in the project.
#
# Do not narrow this rule to specific subfolders. Anything dropped into
# Archive/ must stay off GitHub by default — that is the whole point of the
# folder. Archive/ is NOT backed up by git; it lives in OneDrive only.
Archive/

